@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    Job Tracker Pro is a demonstration application created for educational and portfolio purposes.

    This application stores job application data locally using a SQLite database. No information is transmitted to external services, shared with third parties, or collected for marketing purposes.

    Users are responsible for managing and securing any data entered into the application.

    This project was developed using ASP.NET Core MVC, Entity Framework Core, and SQLite to demonstrate full-stack web development concepts.
</p>
